BHP Billiton Suspended Wessels Manganese Operations After Death

-- B y   C a r l i   L o u r e n s
-- 
2011-02-24T06:58:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-24/bhp-billiton-suspended-wessels-manganese-operations-after-death.html
  BHP Billiton Ltd . said it suspended
operations at Wessels manganese mine, part of its Hotazel unit
in  South Africa , after an employee was killed in an accident.  An investigation into the incident has been started, the
company said in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Carli Lourens at 
 clourens@bloomberg.net  